It’s been more than one year since the final movie in the Jurassic World Trilogy, and therefore time for a soft reboot! Let’s swap in a different Marvel actor, mutate some dinosaurs and have some fun!

Jurassic World Rebirth definitely raises some questions. Like how many islands did these scientists have going? Why is their system designed to release all the dinosaurs at the slightest malfunction? Why was the family on the water, and why are they in this movie?

To answer all of these questions and more, step inside Ryan George’s Pitch Meeting for Jurassic World Rebirth!
